---
title: Thai-Spiced Pork Tacos with Tangy Rainbow Slaw for Dinner with a Sweet Chilli Pork Rice Bowl for Lunch
description: Cook once, with a twist for lunch. Cook an amazing dinner as usual then put a new twist on the recipe to create something different for lunch the next day! Enjoy pork tacos with rainbow slaw, pickled onion and cucumber for dinner, then follow it up with a super-tasty pork and rice bowl for lunch. Extra delicious!

